      "body" : "If you only see 8 connections, it is because you only have 8 outbound connections (which is limited to 8, and it should), and no incoming connections (because of a firewall issue).\r\n\r\nYour patch changes the number of outgoing connections. Yes this will mean more total connections as well, but that is not the correct way to achieve it. The solution is fixing your firewall.",
